<div class="long-content main" role="main">
<h1>Unbroken chains: The curse of modern day slavery in Sindh </h1>
<div class="excerpt-full">
<p>According to the Global Slavery Index 2018, there are over 3 million people under bonded labour in Pakistan </p>
<div class="category-share">
<ul>
<li>
<a target="_blank" href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.geo.tv%2Flatest%2F213723-unbroken-chains-the-curse-of-modern-day-slavery-in-sindh"><img src="https://www.geo.tv/assets/front/images/longfacebook.svg"> </a>
</li>
<li>
<a target="_blank" href="https://twitter.com/share?text=Unbroken chains: The curse of modern day slavery in Sindh &amp;url=https://www.geo.tv/latest/213723-unbroken-chains-the-curse-of-modern-day-slavery-in-sindh"><img src="https://www.geo.tv/assets/front/images/twitter.svg"> </a>
</li>
